// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0291 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: b6497977-fe96-55a8-ba53-d31d44328df9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
